latestPosts.caption:
Our Champions, Together! 🦁🇿🇦

A massive congratulations to our DP World Lions Cricket stars, Kagiso Rabada, Temba Bavuma, Ryan Rickelton and Wiaan Mulder who were part of the Proteas team that triumphed in the ICC World Test Championship Final! 🏆 

Yesterday’s celebrations in London were made even more special as these champions took a moment to celebrate with our Lions Cricket CEO, Jono Leaf-Wright. Such a proud and unforgettable moment for our Union and Country 🏏🦁🇿🇦

The entire Lions family are immensely proud of you and thank you for flying our flag high on the world stage! ✨🤗😃

#LionsCricket #ThePrideOfJozi #TheSpiritOfChampions
#WTCFinalChampions
